Arthur Brock:

"In the [[Metacurrency Project]], we’re committed to practicing what we preach, or eating our own dog food, if you prefer that way of saying it. So as we release Ceptr and the tools we’ve been incubating for the past decade, we are also launching a new organizational model to hold the code, assets and coding community that we see emerging. At the moment we’re calling it Source Tree Commons, and it will be the first [[Sovereign Accountable Commons]] launched."
